{"tid":2276024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE〈I Can't Stop Me〉MV 破億　在音樂節目也成為三冠王啦！","createTime":"2020-11-07T15:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T19:52:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0df0965f49057b1f36e81e19b633204adabe11cc","tid":2276024,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_75960624653c3ab14a2d009109ad0162/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-07/131474-883763.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_75960624653c3ab14a2d009109ad0162%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-07%2F131474-883763.png&h=aeb1daba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在回歸將滿兩週之際，TWICE 除了連續三天征服音樂節目，最新主打歌的 MV 也破億了！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在今天（7 日）凌晨四點左右時，TWICE 的最新主打歌 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 官方 MV 觀看次數跨越了一億大關，距離公開日才剛過 11 天左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6bfe7df1a8c825d3bef5028a053364c5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-07/131474-883761.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6bfe7df1a8c825d3bef5028a053364c5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-07%2F131474-883761.jpeg&h=b5e8c788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 是 TWICE 第三張正規專輯〈Eyes wide open〉的主打歌，融合美國 80 年代的合成器音效和復古的 Synthwave 元素，再度挑戰了新風格。如此一來，TWICE 從出道曲 &ldquo;Like OHH-AHH&rdquo; 至今發行過的 14 支韓語主打歌 MV 都已全數破億。<br />\n<br />\n在這同時，TWICE 這週也接連征服 MBC Music《Show Champion》、Mnet《M! Countdown》和 KBS 2TV《Music Bank》，一轉眼就成為三冠王了！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"0959a28625e5c9a1594842a10b24f299f75d82cf","tid":2276024,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"TWICE win again <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab4